OL,3,C'Hike hat-trick' hits energy customers
OL,5,FThis news has been heart sinking and
OL,6,Ffinance sinking for many. Millions are
OL,7,Falready in energy debt and even though
OL,8,Faverage wages have risen, so too have
OL,9,Fessentials. As the energy increases
OL,10,Farrive in April, so do water bill
OL,11,Frises averaging #123 more each year.
OL,12,FFood costs are still one of the
OL,13,Fbiggest factors in rising inflation
OL,14,Fand now we get this energy bill rise
OL,15,Ffor millions of customers.
OL,17,FImproving peace prospects in Ukraine
OL,18,Fcould lower energy prices this summer.
OL,19,FBefore then, customers must bear the
OL,20,Fbrunt of cold - and of these higher
OL,21,Fcosts
